experiment_description: Experiment with different probabilities of mutation when generating new programs
grammar:
1: Program = begin
    state = Init
    Statement
    End
end
2: Init = mc_init(start_pos)
3: InnerStatement = mc_move!(state, Direction, Times, Sprint, Jump, Sneak)
4: InnerStatement = begin
    InnerStatement
    InnerStatement
end
5: InnerStatement = if Bool
    Statement
end
6: Statement = InnerStatement
7: Statement = begin
    Statement
    Statement
end
8: Statement = while true
    InnerStatement
    Bool || break
end
9: End = mc_end(state)
10: Direction = ["forward"]
11: Direction = ["back"]
12: Direction = ["left"]
13: Direction = ["right"]
14: Direction = ["forward", "left"]
15: Direction = ["forward", "right"]
16: Direction = ["back", "left"]
17: Direction = ["back", "right"]
18: Sprint = 1
19: Jump = 1
20: Sneak = 0
21: Times = 1
22: Times = 2
23: Times = 3
24: Times = 4
25: Bool = is_done(state)
26: Bool = !Bool
27: End = mc_end(state)
28: Bool = mc_was_good_move(state)
29: Bool = mc_has_moved(state)
